label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/medals/
description: Return a list of medals the character has.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/notifications/
description: Return character notifications.This route is cached for up to 600 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/notifications/contacts/
description: Return notifications about having been added to someone's contact list.This route is cached for up to 600 seconds.

label: get /v2/characters/{character_id}/portrait/
description: Get portrait urls for a character.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/roles/
description: Returns a character's corporation roles.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/standings/
description: Return character standings from agents, NPC corporations, and factions.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/titles/
description: Returns a character's titles.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/names/
description: Resolve a set of character IDs to character names.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: post /v3/characters/{character_id}/cspa/
description: Takes a source character ID in the url and a set of target character ID's in the body, returns a CSPA charge cost.

label: post /v1/characters/affiliation/
description: Bulk lookup of character IDs to corporation, alliance and faction.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v2/characters/{character_id}/clones/
description: A list of the character's clones.This route is cached for up to 120 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/implants/
description: Return implants on the active clone of a character.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: delete /v1/characters/{character_id}/contacts/
description: Bulk delete contacts.

label: get /v1/alliances/{alliance_id}/contacts/
description: Return contacts of an alliance.This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/contacts/
description: Return contacts of a character.This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/contacts/labels/
description: Return custom labels for contacts the character defined.This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: get /v1/corporations/{corporation_id}/contacts/
description: Return contacts of a corporation.This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: post /v1/characters/{character_id}/contacts/
description: Bulk add contacts with same settings.

label: put /v1/characters/{character_id}/contacts/
description: Bulk edit contacts with same settings.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/contracts/
description: Returns contracts available to a character, only if the character is issuer, acceptor or assignee. Only returns contracts no older than 30 days, or if the status is "in_progress".This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/contracts/{contract_id}/bids/
description: Lists bids on a particular auction contract.This route is cached for up to 300 seconds.

label: get /v1/characters/{character_id}/contracts/{contract_id}/items/
description: Lists items of a particular contract.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/corporations/{corporation_id}/contracts/
description: Returns contracts available to a coporation, only if the corporation is issuer, acceptor or assignee. Only returns contracts no older than 30 days, or if the status is "in_progress".This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/corporations/{corporation_id}/contracts/{contract_id}/bids/
description: Lists bids on a particular auction contract.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.

label: get /v1/corporations/{corporation_id}/contracts/{contract_id}/items/
description: Lists items of a particular contract.This route is cached for up to 3600 seconds.
